title: Carol Burnett Show Collector's Edition (27 of 31 Discs)
description:
In the early part of the 2000s Guthy-Renker released "The Carol Burnett Show Collector's Edition" DVD set of 31 discs, with two full episodes on each, mostly from seasons 7-10. These 62 episodes were supposedly hand picked by the cast as their favorites of all time. The first ten volumes had brief interview segments with Burnett, Korman, and Conway before and after each episode.

The original uploader of these discs had defective discs 3,6,8,26 that could not be used. Therefore, only 27 of the 31 discs sold to the public, are available here.

I have made several corrections to the episode list which was in the previous torrent that I am replacing with this one.
